title: Raspberry Jello Mousse- only 2 ww points
directions: Add boiling water to jello mix in large mixing bowl. Stir till jello is dissolved completely. Add ice; stir until completely melted. Gently stir in 1 1/2 cups each of cool whip and berries until well blended.
Spoon into dessert dishes. Refrigerate for 2 hours or until firm.
Garnish with Cool Whip and Raspberries.
ingredients: 2 cups thawed Cool Whip Fat Free whipped topping
